146
00:07:11,529 --> 00:07:13,330
Court ordered, Mr. Freely?

147
00:07:13,330 --> 00:07:17,383
Yeah, Rosie got a DUI three years ago.

148
00:07:17,383 --> 00:07:18,474
Judge didn't take the kid away,

149
