242
00:11:14,366 --> 00:11:15,441
I hear men voices.

243
00:11:15,441 --> 00:11:16,377
The night she died?

244
00:11:16,377 --> 00:11:20,131
Yeah. In and out, climb up, 
down the stairs.

245
00:11:20,131 --> 00:11:22,342
You didn't mention that two years ago.

246
00:11:23,487 --> 00:11:24,818
I see black run.

247
00:11:24,818 --> 00:11:25,992
I told about black.

248
00:11:25,992 --> 00:11:27,831
Black did it.

249
00:11:29,243 --> 00:11:31,834
You see men come up in 
this place a lot, Tammy?

250
00:11:31,834 --> 00:11:33,014
No.

251
00:11:33,014 --> 00:11:36,049
But one bedroom apartment... come on.

252
00:11:36,049 --> 00:11:38,607
Toya sleeps on the couch, I think.

253
00:11:38,607 --> 00:11:40,017
Wait. Rosie made her kid

254
00:11:40,017 --> 00:11:41,890
sleep in the living room?

255
00:11:43,357 --> 00:11:47,324
So Rosie keep the bedroom 
for herself for reason, no?

256
00:11:49,843 --> 00:11:52,294
But I don't make judgement.

257
00:11:52,294 --> 00:11:54,456
Like you are.

258
00:11:55,119 --> 00:11:56,615
Like now.

259
00:11:59,326 --> 00:12:01,308
We got a uniform 
posted at the hospital?

260
00:12:01,308 --> 00:12:03,249
Yeah. No visitors for Rosie yet.

261
00:12:03,249 --> 00:12:04,179
No family?

262
00:12:04,179 --> 00:12:06,594
Mm-mm. Parents are dead.

263
00:12:07,089 --> 00:12:09,082
This job ain't coming in, boss.

264
00:12:09,082 --> 00:12:10,511
We got nothing.

265
00:12:10,511 --> 00:12:12,024
We got a witness.

266
00:12:12,024 --> 00:12:13,679
Whose hard drive's been erased.

267
00:12:13,679 --> 00:12:14,895
"Bruises and butterflies",

268
